title: London Goheen shows off her derriere as she cooks wearing a G-STRING
text:
Anything Tammy Hembrow can do, London Goheen thinks she can do better.

On Tuesday, Tammy's ex-Reece Hawkins' model girlfriend turned up the heat by wearing a G-string in the kitchen.

Taking to Instagram, the 21-year-old shared a racy photo while cooking and showing off her derriere in barely-there bottoms and a crop top.

Turning up the heat! Reece Hawkins' model girlfriend London Goheen (pictured) has showed off her derriere while cooking in a G-STRING

The model oozed sex appeal as she seductively glanced at the camera while striking a sultry pose in the kitchen.

'Hanging around the boyfriend too long will get you a booty for sure,' she captioned the post.

She accessorised her raunchy ensemble with a pair of white sneakers and wore her glossy dark hair down past her shoulders.

Confident! London shared a racy photo flaunting her derriere in barely-there bottoms and a crop top

London's post came just hours after her boyfriend's ex Tammy Hembrow made jaws drop, posing in a 'naked bikini'.

The 25-year-old Instagram model shared a photo while wearing the skimpy swimsuit and glancing into the distance.

Tammy's swimmers featured tiny g-string bottoms and a triangle-style top that barely covered her cleavage.

Posing for the camera side on, Tammy made sure to flaunt her famous backside and buxom bust.

Can't be missed! London's post came just hours after Reece's ex Tammy Hembrow (pictured) made jaws drop, posing in a 'naked bikini'

It's over! Tammy and Reece were together for almost five years and share custody of daughter Saskia, two, and son Wolf, four (pictured)

Meanwhile, it has been over a year since Tammy announced her split from ex-fiance and father of her two children, Reece,n in June 2018.

The former couple, who were together for almost five years, currently share custody of daughter Saskia, two, and son Wolf, four.

Three months after their split, Reece, 24, debuted his new romance with London in October.

Tammy has also moved on, and has been dating Canadian singer and rapper, Jahkoy Palmer, 25, since June this year.
description: Anything Tammy Hembrow can do, London Goheen thinks she can do better.
authors: Mary Mrad For Daily Mail Australia
